title: WWE Gorilla Position podcast
text:
WWE legend leaves Punk a voicemail message 
The panel discuss the rivalry between Kevin Owens and Goldberg , the Raw Women's Title picture and The Rock's interaction with Vince McMahon before Monday's show inside the Staples Center. 
John Cena and The Miz's altercation on Smackdown is also discussed, as is Luke Harper and AJ Styles fighting to a draw in a Battle Royal to determine Bray Wyatt's WrestleMania 33 challenger. Luke Harper and AJ Styles will go one-on-one next week 
Elsewhere, Ash Rose chats to Scottish star Wolfgang about reaching the semi-finals of the United Kingdom Championship Tournament, Tyler Bate and his earliest WWE memories. 
For all that, plus even more gimmicks being banished to the Hall of Shame, download Gorilla Position now! http://www.skysports.com/podcasts/gorilla-position Live WWE Late Night Raw February 28, 2017, 1:00am
